TO DEPLOY:
- clone submodules (library | public/nwPublicLibrary)
	run these commands from your project root directory:
		rm -r public/nwPublicLibrary
		git clone git@github.com:NovumWare/NovumWarePublicLibrary.git public/nwPublicLibrary
		rm -r library
		git clone git@github.com:NovumWare/Zend_Library.git library
- create MySQL DB and update Database Setup in application/configs/local_settings.ini
- create log file with write permission at logs/log.txt
	run these commands from the project root directory:
		mkdir logs
		chmod -R 777 logs
		touch logs/log.txt
- create Smarty temp folder with write permission at tmp/templates_c
	run these commands from the project root directory:
		mkdir tmp
		mkdir tmp/templates_c
		chmod -R 777 tmp/templates_c
- copy file and update @siteRoot in the newly copied file
	run these commands from the project root directory
		cp SETUP/local_variables.less public/stylesheets/less/local_variables.less
- define $_sessionNamespace in the bootstrap